Hire additional qualified staff in the Accounting Office to handle records of economic enterprises;

Require the Municipal Accountant to maintain a complete set of subsidiary ledgers for the above-mentioned Special Accounts in the General Fund and to prepare separate financial statements thereof at year-end pursuant to Section 313 of RA No. 7160 and pertinent provisions of NGAS Manual, Vol. I. for monitoring and control purposes;

Require the Municipal Budget Office to include the operating cost appropriation of Terminal, Market and Slaughter operations in the preparation of annual budget; and

Request the Sangguniang Bayan of Donsol to pass an ordinance declaring the aforesaid five (5) operation as Economic Enterprises of the Municipality.

